description:
If you are looking for very special bracelets, these are for you.
 
"Kazaz wire" is the primary material used to create this type of exquisite and unique jewelry, the so called "Kazaziye". A strand of 24 K gold or 1000 K silver having only 0.008 micron thickness (as fine as one strand of human hair) is wrapped over a very thin silk thread with the help of a spinning wheel. Finished Kazaz wire is flexible, yet very strong.
